item.title: CVE-2022-29509|2024-08-03T06:26:05.979Z -- t%26d%20corporation -- t%26d%20data%20server%20and%20thermo%20recorder%20data%20server
item.description: Directory traversal vulnerability in T&D Data Server (Japanese Edition) Ver.2.22 and earlier, T&D Data Server (English Edition) Ver.2.30 and earlier, THERMO RECORDER DATA SERVER (Japanese Edition) Ver.2.13 and earlier, and THERMO RECORDER DATA SERVER (English Edition) Ver.2.13 and earlier allows a remote attacker to view an arbitrary file on the server via unspecified vectors.
